c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F221105_2b5fd0a36a266ad6af3b642da942d52c.jpg&h=7d7fa3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越戰時期，一個越共狙擊手對美軍軍營開槍，美軍唔知佢嘅位置，所以出現以上畫面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個鐘之後，美軍上山調查，搵唔到佢條屍體，原因不明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比美軍生食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa3cd5e26614a801539e4da08574379a3a6d2dd","tid":230550,"uid":34623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打得多battlefield都知sniper多數冇好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成撚日比人刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"76f976edd19df3957cb17190c2676fdaf7bc81f3","tid":230550,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你睇多D狙擊片都知狙擊手通常得幾條友，打唔中通常都死，人地一架車或者直昇機沖埋黎乜都死</blockquote><br />\nV字手勢由來<br />\n就知狙擊手比人捉到 死得最慘</blockquote><br />\n狙擊手比人捉到唔止斬兩隻手指</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nV手指來源係英國長弓兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bafa8a0537b170396a75a4b2a454a31f2eff78","tid":230550,"uid":101550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你睇多D狙擊片都知狙擊手通常得幾條友，打唔中通常都死，人地一架車或者直昇機沖埋黎乜都死</blockquote><br />\nV字手勢由來<br />\n就知狙擊手比人捉到 死得最慘</blockquote><br />\nv字手勢係起源於百年戰爭<br />\n法國人會斬左英國弓兵兩隻手指等佢冇得再拉弓<br />\nv字手勢代表上次戰伇冇俾人捉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35672bcf5b7d62bffc82cb9d9d66df080faa9cf","tid":230550,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸無人機果條友先係</blockquote><br />\n呢個答案我真係buy!"},{"pid":"5c9c0554999477a6fa99a4414de5e0d99df89216","tid":230550,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚西咩 狙擊手 通常做recon  除非有敵人見到啦<br />\n城市戰 又通常係支援地面突擊隊 你企高位 而且通常有助手 或有一team人<br />\n最後就係睇邊國家的狙擊手 美軍ge話 好安全啦 大把back up 又UAV 有敵人上黎搵你都通晒水</blockquote><br />\n狙擊手係步兵對步兵嘅時候優先清除嘅目標<br />\n同揸機槍一樣係第一個受靶<br />\n所以一開槍就等於叫人射你"},{"pid":"9644b382627096f1e0fb67271fa3a160fbc845bd","tid":230550,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"係現代化軍隊（中美俄...），大多狙擊手都變成咗炮擊觀察員，好少開槍殺人了"},{"pid":"957ffa5397b94ff6847df53c9a42d0aaf28adb01","tid":230550,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"話你on9怕你嬲"},{"pid":"9226b487ff974372d23581ea80a9a1a6de7cb5d2","tid":230550,"uid":12755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"你估打cs咩"},{"pid":"f575c7332642228d70a22a590be40b091a05d6dd","tid":230550,"uid":22696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"指揮官？"},{"pid":"81af99618689d9f5cd4d7f84a94e7c1673a1049a","tid":230550,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揸無人機果條友先係</blockquote><br />\n呢個答案我真係buy!</blockquote><br />\n依d半後勤就唔計啦，你不如講埋㩒發射飛彈果d發射員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c141621dbb311e1eea4801a4d3bb5c747eb55b7","tid":230550,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"你唔肯定個一槍殺到人你都唔會安全"},{"pid":"7110501407012f358513666c2e14e752176c3709","tid":230550,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a19c64c4ea5dac1ae38e3e54d1c506775ccef91","tid":230550,"uid":12705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/221101_5664281425cea3cfd96d0f663e51a071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F221101_5664281425cea3cfd96d0f663e51a071.jpg&h=8c08f08f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zn1023Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZn1023Y.jpg&h=c2a204b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Z9ZN1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Z9ZN1d.jpg&h=5679cf0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/221105_2b5fd0a36a266ad6af3b642da942d52c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F221105_2b5fd0a36a266ad6af3b642da942d52c.jpg&h=7d7fa3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越戰時期，一個越共狙擊手對美軍軍營開槍，美軍唔知佢嘅位置，所以出現以上畫面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個鐘之後，美軍上山調查，搵唔到佢條屍體，原因不明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比美軍生食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美軍有on9仔喺營玩槍走火<br />\n賴落越共到"},{"pid":"47ac0ced28050984fe62837669d22190ba96d852","tid":230550,"uid":48899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開完槍人地成大隊人追你一個，你要幾近冇support下自己走佬都咪話唔驚</blockquote><br />\n驚閪咩 我八百里外一槍打瓜佢 之後跛嘅都走得甩啦</blockquote><br />\n1里=500米，咩槍射到咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學家1 里點500 米呀"},{"pid":"70f6b0a9ad3d112572b215c20fa50050a2a7c478","tid":230550,"uid":48899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩講狙擊手既電影介紹 除左American sniper</blockquote><br />\n有套好似係二戰，１個年輕既狙擊手同1個老將軍狙擊手大鬥法，想搵番黎睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEnemy at the Gates (2001)</blockquote><br />\n呢套勁正</blockquote><br />\nEnermy at the Gates <br />\n優質電影"},{"pid":"4f2fa7038643fcfdf1ccba83ce07962ac0a3cd28","tid":230550,"uid":45350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"Imagine yourself as a sniper.<br />\n<br />\nYou know who I am, and you&rsquo;ve been ordered to shoot me on sight.<br />\n<br />\nYou&rsquo;ve positioned yourself on a high ridge, you are well-hidden, and keeping constant watch on the area.<br />\n<br />\nYou see me, I am six hundred meters away.<br />\n<br />\nYou take aim, you start calculating all of the variables. You wait for me to stop moving to make your shot easier. I stop to talk to one of my subordinates, you hold your breath&hellip;and you die.<br />\n<br />\nWhy are you dead?<br />\n<br />\nBecause I have a sniper too. Unlike you, my sniper lives here. He knows the area better than you, and he knows every place you might post-up. He already suspected you were there. The moment you started moving to take aim at me, he saw you.<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s go further.<br />\n<br />\nMy sniper doesn&rsquo;t see you, or maybe it just happens to be his day-off. You take aim, you feel the recoil of the rifle, and you see me fall over. All those guys in dirty uniforms standing around me are now very angry that you shot the commanding officer. They&rsquo;re coming for you. They outnumber you. They have vehicles, you can&rsquo;t outrun them.<br />\n<br />\nYou start putting shots into the radiators of my comrades trucks so they can&rsquo;t pursue you. And then you die.<br />\n<br />\nWhy are you dead?<br />\n<br />\nBecause you fired enough times for the guys seeking to avenge me to get a rough idea of where you were. They called their friends over at artillery and with guns that have a much longer range than yours, they dropped shells on your position. None of them hit you directly&hellip;but they didn&rsquo;t need to.<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s go further&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nMy guys had no artillery available. You not only killed me, but you crippled the vehicles they might use to chase you. You have a huge head-start, so you retreat before they get close enough to figure out where you are.<br />\n<br />\nYou&rsquo;re running through the jungle, you&rsquo;ve got to stay ahead before you&rsquo;re up to your ass in men who want your blood. And then you die.<br />\n<br />\nWhy are you dead?<br />\n<br />\nYou missed the land mine, booby-trap, or other no-tresspassing device in your exfiltration route.<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s go further&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nYou found and avoid all the traps, you got away from the men who want your blood. You&rsquo;re almost at the rendezvous point where a chopper is waiting to get you out of this hellhole.<br />\n<br />\nYou board the chopper, you breath a sigh of relief, you take off and head home. Then you die.<br />\n<br />\nWhy are you dead?<br />\n<br />\nA random patrol of guys, not even part of my unit happened by, and just happened to have a missile launcher on hand. Now you&rsquo;re part of the burning wreck falling from the sky.<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s go further&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nThere is no patrol with a missile-launcher. You fly on, you&rsquo;re halfway back to base. You&rsquo;ve been itching for a cigarette, and finally feel safe enough to light one up. You strike the match, and then you die.<br />\n<br />\nWhy are you dead?<br />\n<br />\nBecause life&rsquo;s a bitch, something broke on your helicopter and you crashed. No enemy action, just bad luck and mechanical failure.<br />\n<br />\nYes I know, this is an over-simplified, over-dramatized version. But the points are valid. The fact a sniper has distance between him and his targets offers him some leeway, but it does not mean his job is safe, that it is without risk, or that he is not in immediate danger the entire time. There are a lot of ways to die in a battlefield, and snipers are vulnerable to most of them.<br />\n<br />\nEdit"},{"pid":"e7c07cbc8c09865fe23dcf6d757efd02c28c49a7","tid":230550,"uid":10409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"上面篇文太長唔quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路睇一路好似玩緊dumb ways to die咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4559696271def02a2836daae6783d31ad24171","tid":230550,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士即係樓豬你應該最安全"},{"pid":"2e6c29b5bdc10d6e7b69d0204c5a73725a1304fa","tid":230550,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"850055aeabd96784a0015c086659ccb4d27a6f16","tid":230550,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca852bb9723c6f2474cfde034ba8ed00b26dae55","tid":230550,"uid":20430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"係高登講過連登講多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狙擊手主要任務係地面部隊無法直接進入範圍，狙擊手會負責清除障礙及暗殺目標，多半為1人至2人行動。然而狙擊手其實沒有大家想像咁有效率同速度兵種。<br />\n<br />\n一般狙擊手多半為地面部隊支援。而作為隊伍中偵察部隊，多半會先於地面部隊抵達戰場，如果以對方基地為起點的話，一般個設置一個狙擊點，而距離一般為800咪至1000咪不等(但基本狙擊範圍一般600咪左右)<br />\n<br />\n然後就係可能用極長時間，慢慢...慢慢...慢慢咁潛行爬行到狙擊地點，當中既慢係要潛行時令敵方不發現狙擊手到達戰場，過程中可能一個鐘頭內先移動少少<br />\n<br />\n千辛萬苦去到，再Setup好狙擊點，計算好距離，計算當時風速影響以及計算彈道距離。<br />\n<br />\n當完成以上準備後，就要預算好幾條逃走路線，係我無打錯係逃走路線。狙擊手基本作用只有一擊逃離作戰方式，點解會咁講我為大家講解。<br />\n<br />\n首先，狙擊鏡其實沒有大家玩開遊戲中咁輕鬆靈活，狙擊手帶上裝備及狙擊鏡等等重量其實遠超大家想像，無法快速狙擊連續射擊是事實。<br />\n<br />\n其次為聲浪，狙擊鏡因為用上大口徑彈藥關係，就算如上面提到例子800咪開槍打向基地，但基本上一開槍全山頭都知你係邊度，然後就一堆高射砲、砲台等等聖誕節煙花式招呼到你頭上。所以基本上狙擊手狙擊後會立即離開射擊點，以逃避敵方追擊步隊<br />\n<br />\n而就算一般單兵作戰，基本上有接受訓練士兵，一般不會係同一地點長期開火作戰，因為會暴露身藏位置。所以由其機動性更低狙擊手，基本上開完一槍，極小同一位置再開槍，而係離開狙擊位置。<br />\n<br />\n應該會有巴打異議，有滅聲管呢樣野喎，我就老實話你知，滅聲管只係減低聲浪，而唔係好似一般遊戲中完全無聲，基本有一定聲浪。另一個問題就係滅聲管其實消耗性係相當大既物品所以長期作戰，如果對上一團軍隊的話，狙擊手是相當不利。<br />\n<br />\n所以扣除以上不利狙擊手條件，地面部隊中通常重有一個士兵安排為精準射手，其裝備上相對輕鬆於狙擊槍，多半以長步槍作為狙擊步槍，得到機動性的精準射手，多半同時配合地面部隊推進戰場。<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再幻想狙擊手有幾輕鬆拎起支槍就搞掂，現實當中需要好多時間耐力同能力先成功完成一次狙擊。<br />\n<br />\n最安全緊係將軍啦，係軍情處嘆住冷氣對住個Mon就已經可以打飛機，又唔洗佢做，幾爽？任務完成又可以交代收工，任務失敗又唔洗佢死，直頭佢玩曬啦。"},{"pid":"2c9cf526ca33e0b50a4815ef4a30c53b0ab2d2e5","tid":230550,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"Sniper係smoke可以睇到敵人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 rainbow six 玩家"},{"pid":"dd55615449d51214d9ce12713232b50a214fe0d0","tid":230550,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"Sniper 通常都會仲有個哨兵（OP point)幫你睇位<br />\n<br />\n點會一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ：表哥係sdu"},{"pid":"2ba323e7a467ae86dd24868dea26ae3158727387","tid":230550,"uid":107461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e8683083ad894f34523af107ba6e090b7951254","tid":230550,"uid":6647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"諗起有套又係打仗既電影(唔記得咩名)<br />\n揸無人機去殺武裝份子<br />\n食住薯片飲可樂睇住個mon同控制搖控桿好似打機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5621a49fa4b9fa2b1d8dbf18ade4df80de15332e","tid":230550,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:44:02.000Z","msg":"其實咪出咗套戲講美國神狙，睇下咪知佢幾安全或其他同袍點墊底？"},{"pid":"e3e45df406ec0ffd856e255dde5b3fb221d44bcb","tid":230550,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"美軍咁先進，而家啲狙擊手係咪多數都係做先頭部隊做測量call人空襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad13a0ec53ca4c57e9234d50431a44812284f046","tid":230550,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">華西里扎斯夫</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981fae543386122758eb07cb62ce4244ac9c76d0","tid":230550,"uid":16477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"多數狙撃手都係殺唔到人 主角用手槍一個華麗轉身反而可以爆尻狙擊手頭"},{"pid":"6d5b22d8892b4f0a09f05c70e199cd3a4cf8ebf9","tid":230550,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sniper 通常都會仲有個哨兵（OP point)幫你睇位<br />\n<br />\n點會一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ：表哥係sdu</blockquote><br />\n軍隊同警察既狙擊手好唔同"},{"pid":"a985109db1bc8f72ba2d59d58da2ae3eb5c0eba9","tid":230550,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sniper 通常都會仲有個哨兵（OP point)幫你睇位<br />\n<br />\n點會一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 ：表哥係sdu</blockquote><br />\n軍事特種部隊同特警執行嘅任務完全唔同<br />\n面對嘅威脅都唔同<br />\n冇類比性"},{"pid":"45e9c3bb3f1ae7568320b785444eb2712b6cbd9a","tid":230550,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無咩講狙擊手既電影介紹 除左American sniper</blockquote><br />\n有套好似係二戰，１個年輕既狙擊手同1個老將軍狙擊手大鬥法，想搵番黎睇</blockquote><br />\n兵臨城下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4df09bfce256386fe68241c73a2ec3bf8377df","tid":230550,"uid":114563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"理性討論?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696800a9679478c13ce3f8fcaf9361cefd55af51","tid":230550,"uid":104676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無咩講狙擊手既電影介紹 除左American sniper</blockquote><br />\n有套好