high value target<br />\n被對家捉到下場慘過好多人<br />\n加上出得狙擊手就即係大部隊甚至小隊都出唔到<br />\n好似USMC force recon呢類<br />\n出到去真係得個shooter同spotter<br />\n被人一圍就係咁先<br />\n又要長期保持同一姿勢<br />\n生理同心理負擔都好大"},{"pid":"b01440157c1017992f8abf53a6815d077de27fcf","tid":230550,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n步槍同狙擊槍結構有咩唔同？點解步槍可以發揮狙擊槍嘅功能仲唔會被人發現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁狙擊槍咪喪失咗存在嘅意義？"},{"pid":"1a779c5b0e002020ffc955a02dc6fea7dca7a916","tid":230550,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n步槍同狙擊槍結構有咩唔同？點解步槍可以發揮狙擊槍嘅功能仲唔會被人發現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁狙擊槍咪喪失咗存在嘅意義？</blockquote><br />\n狙擊槍其實係叫狙擊<span style=\"color: red;\">步</span>槍<br />\n基本上就係槍管長啲既步槍"}]}